name: FANTA
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
What is the project about?
FANTA IS MEME 

What makes your project unique?
It is a MEME token with low price impact because it provides a lot of initial liquidity and is launched. We partnered with the POLONIEX exchange and listed it.

History of your project.
It was launched through UNISWAP on May 22, 2023 and listed on the global exchange POLONIEX in 3 days.

What’s next for your project?
We have plans to list on more exchanges. We are already talking about listing with MEXC HUOBI KUCOIN BITMART GATE IO.

What can your token be used for?
Our token goes beyond simple MEME and we plan to create a staking DEFI system.
